message.body: Hey Zach, I'm frying up some SC caught bass tonight. sorry for the short notice but I wasn't sure if I had enough fish. Versek can't make it so you are welcome to come. I however don't have a lot of fish so please don't bring a crowd of you can come
Thanks for the invite! I'm in maine tho, eating oysters and scallops.
